{
  "stem": "16790.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 293.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I would say, well, it's hard for me to judge at that time, but it was quite a distance out.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they had these little boats, but the boats-- the little boats were close.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so I thought, hey, you know, somebody could jump overboard and get on one of those little boats and then-- not realizing you need the papers and that type of thing.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I mean, I had no idea about those things.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were a couple, not very many.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I remember seeing them go down onto a tender and then going into Havana.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we all wondered, why are they the lucky ones?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I don't know-- I don't know how or why they were allowed to get off.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I think it that-- there wasn't much hostility, there wasn't too much anger.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was just tremendous fear.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I remember walking-- people walking around and talking.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And some women were crying as to what are we going to do now, what's going to happen to us?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this-- this constant stress that they were living under was very difficult for them to cope.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, once we departed again Havana harbor, they-- they were seasick and their immediate concern was fighting the seasickness.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I do recall my mother saying, things are-- don't worry-- telling me, don't worry, things are gonna be OK, things are going to work out.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, she probably said that to alleviate the fears of a little boy.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I don't know how she personally felt, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And once we got to Miami, I said, well, here, we can come in this way.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My-- it was very difficult to talk to my mother about those times.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She clammed up.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
